  "text": "While the fluid flow in the PMMA channel is fully attached, the flow over the packaged TMCF sensors can be either separated or attached [CITATION_1] . In this paper, a reduced chip Reynolds number Re * was used to characterize the flow separation, as shown in equation (1) .",
